{"ID":"20260305082130-c4p6j76","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-c4p6j76","title":"类模板","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-jsgqqd6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-jsgqqd6"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 类模板\ndate created: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 11:33:36 中午\ndate modified: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 11:15:04 晚上\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-98fyha1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-98fyha1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 类模版的定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-jw63ql5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-jw63ql5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类模板是\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e参数化的类\u003c/font\u003e，即用于实现数据类型参数化的类。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-rxotvxi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-rxotvxi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用类模板可以使类中的数据成员、函数成员的参数及函数成员的返回值能根据模板参数匹配情况取任意数据类型。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ximlz5q","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ximlz5q","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"template \u003c模板形参表\u003e \nclass ClassName {\n    //...\n};\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qt8omds","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qt8omds","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026lt;模板形参表\u0026gt;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 与"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-3m0qivo","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"函数模板"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相同语法相同。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以使用却缺省的类型参数"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"template \u0026lt;class T = int\u0026gt;"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-oit28ti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-oit28ti","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"举例"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gf9kl2w","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gf9kl2w","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"template \u003cclass T\u003e  \nclass VECTOR { \nprivate: \n    T *data; \n    int size;  \npublic:  \n    VECTOR(int); \n    ~VECTOR();  \n    T \u0026 operator[](int);  \n    VECTOR \u0026 operator=(const VECTOR \u0026 a);\n};\n\n// 在类体外实现函数的语法\ntemplate \u003cclass T\u003e VECTOR\u003cT\u003e::VECTOR(int n) // 构造函数  \n{ data = new T[size=n]; }  \n\ntemplate\u003cclass T\u003e VECTOR\u003cT\u003e::~VECTOR( ) // 析构函数 \n{ delete []data; }  \n\ntemplate\u003cclass T\u003e T \u0026 VECTOR\u003cT\u003e::operator[ ](int i)  \n{ return data[i]; }  \n\ntemplate \u003cclass T\u003e VECTOR\u003cT\u003e \u0026 VECTOR\u003cT\u003e:: operator=(const VECTOR \u0026 a)  \n{ ... }\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-eww10ns","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-eww10ns","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 类模版的使用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-didtzau","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-didtzau","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void main() { \nVECTOR\u003cint\u003e LI(20);\nVECTOR\u003cdouble\u003e LD(30);\nLI[0] = 10;\nLI[1] = 20;\nint z=LI[0] + LI[1];\ncout \u003c\u003c z \u003c\u003c endl; // 显示30\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dcmijdm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dcmijdm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 类模版的特点"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-if1g8qm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-if1g8qm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-6q3u9ke","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6q3u9ke","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-po20e87","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-po20e87","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类模板自身并不产生代码；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cwn2pa3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cwn2pa3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-behylyc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-behylyc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"它指定类的一个家族；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-vphgbs3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vphgbs3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-w6l2d91","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-w6l2d91","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当引用时，才产生代码，生成模板类。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dh2o2fs","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dh2o2fs","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 类模版与"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082131-2dyp7kf","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"继承"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-pak1rxl","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pak1rxl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vyw2iel","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vyw2iel","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-q5gf4h3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-q5gf4h3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类模板可以从类模板派生"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-yz42vt2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-yz42vt2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-azabp3i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properti